00:35:06,720 --> 00:35:07,040
 kaže,

537
00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:07,900
 dođi ovam,

538
00:35:07,900 --> 00:35:08,620
 pusti to,

539
00:35:08,620 --> 00:35:08,860
 kaže,

540
00:35:08,860 --> 00:35:09,280
 bako,

541
00:35:09,280 --> 00:35:10,420
 treba vas nešto stane.

