562
00:35:37,340 --> 00:35:38,380
 to neće biti dobro.

563
00:35:38,500 --> 00:35:39,620
 treba jedno drugo

564
00:35:39,620 --> 00:35:40,400
 podržavati,

565
00:35:40,400 --> 00:35:41,820
 onda na taj način

566
00:35:41,820 --> 00:35:43,720
 razvija se to

567
00:35:43,720 --> 00:35:45,280
 jedno međusobno povjerenje

568
00:35:45,280 --> 00:35:46,880
 i znaš da ne partner

569
00:35:46,880 --> 00:35:48,140
 koji je uz tebe,

570
00:35:48,140 --> 00:35:48,980
 stoji uz tebe

571
00:35:48,980 --> 00:35:49,760
