595
00:36:22,820 --> 00:36:23,500
 i strategija.

596
00:36:23,500 --> 00:36:27,680
 Kad su velikog vojskovođu

597
00:36:27,680 --> 00:36:29,040
 malog čovjeka,

598
00:36:29,040 --> 00:36:30,520
